### 로그인유저의 식재료 정보 등록
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ingredient-stock-service/ingredient-stock
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ingredientStockName": "왕만두",
  "ingredientStockCategory": "processed",
  "ingredientStockBoughtAt": "2026-01-13",
  "ingredientStockExpiredAt": "2028-10-24",
  "ingredientStockTotalCost": 15000,
  "ingredientStockTotalQuantity": 10,
  "ingredientStockUnit": "ea"
}

### 로그인유저 식재료 알림 리스트 세팅
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ingredient-stock-service/ingredient-stock/notification
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}


### 로그인유저의 식재료 정보 수정 (사용한 재료 차감)
PATCH http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ingredient-stock-service/ingredient-stock
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ingredientStockNo": 8,
  "ingredientStockUsedQuantity": 10
}

### 로그인유저의 식재료 리스트 조회
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ingredient-stock-service/ingredient-stocks
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 식재료 폐기 등록 (재고 감소 및 폐기 이력 생성)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ingredient-stock-service/disposal
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ingredientStockNo": 40,
  "disposalQuantity": 5,
  "disposalReason": "유통기한 경과"
}

### 폐기 이력 조회
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ingredient-stock-service/disposals
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

